AddModelRequest, AnyData, ClassificationInferenceRequest, ClearModelRequest, ClipCompareRequest, ClipImageEmbeddingRequest, ClipTextEmbeddingRequest, DoctrOCRInferenceRequest, GazeDetectionInferenceRequest, GroundingDINOInferenceRequest, InferenceRequestImage, InstanceSegmentationInferenceRequest, KeypointsDetectionInferenceRequest, ObjectDetectionInferenceRequest, PredefinedWorkflowDescribeInterfaceRequest, PredefinedWorkflowInferenceRequest, Sam2EmbeddingRequest, Sam2SegmentationRequest, SamEmbeddingRequest, SamSegmentationRequest, TrOCRInferenceRequest, WorkflowsBlocksDescriptionRequest, WorkflowSpecificationDescribeInterfaceRequest, WorkflowSpecificationInferenceRequest, YOLOWorldInferenceRequest
public abstract class RoboflowRequestData extends Object
Abstract class representing request data for Roboflow API operations.
This class provides methods for serializing the request data to different formats such as HTTP request bodies and JSON payloads.
Subclasses of this class represent specific request data types for different Roboflow API requests.

  • Method Details

    • toBodyPublisher

      public HttpRequest.BodyPublisher toBodyPublisher(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper mapper)
      Converts the current request data object to a HttpRequest.BodyPublisher with a JSON payload.
      The JSON payload is serialized using the provided ObjectMapper.
      The JSON content is also saved to a file named "jsonPayload.json" for debugging purposes.
      Parameters:
      mapper - The ObjectMapper used to serialize the request data.
      Returns:
      A HttpRequest.BodyPublisher containing the serialized JSON data.

    • toRequestBody

      public okhttp3.RequestBody toRequestBody(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper mapper)
      Converts the current request data object to a RequestBody for use with RequestSenderOfHttpClient.
      The request body is serialized to JSON format using the provided ObjectMapper.
      Parameters:
      mapper - The ObjectMapper used to serialize the request data.
      Returns:
      A RequestBody containing the serialized JSON data.
